{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_11_02",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 2話 一度懲らしめておかないと",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――里帰りライブ　打ち合わせ当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Homecoming Live Meeting Day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "本日はありがとうございました\n詳細はまた後日、ご連絡させていただきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for today.\nWe'll contact you with the details later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.6,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8566.666666699999,
          "startTime": 13.1666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "失礼します。引き続き、よろしくお願いします\n……ふぅ、なんとかまとまりそうで良かったですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Excuse us. Please continue to work with us.\n…Phew‚ I'm glad it looks like everything will come together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.9333332856
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ。でも思った以上に、注意事項が多かったな……\n怜に来てもらって正解だったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. But there were more things to be careful about than I expected…\nIt was the right choice to have Rei come.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.3999999523
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "私も来て良かったです\nおかげで、より良いステージに出来そうですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm glad I came too.\nThanks to this‚ we can make an even better stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "本当にありがとう、今日は助かったよ\n遅くなったけど、早く実家の方に帰ってあげてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you so much‚ you really helped today.\nIt got late‚ but please hurry home to your family.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.466666619
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんはこの後どうするんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you doing after this‚ {user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.466666619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "せっかく星見市に来たし、以前お世話になった人達に\n挨拶回りをしていこうと思ってるけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since I came all the way to Hoshimi City‚ I thought I'd make\nthe rounds to greet people who helped me before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.4333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.3000022411
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "それなら一緒に行きます\n私もご挨拶したい人達がいるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then I'll go with you.\nI also have people I want to greet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.3666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "家族とは、普段から電話とかでやりとりしてますし\nこういう機会じゃないと挨拶出来ない人達もいますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I keep in touch with my family regularly by phone\nand there are people I can only greet on occasions like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.7333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.9666689078
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（やけに乗り気だけど……なるほどな。怜にとっても）\n（お世話になった人達にお礼を伝えるいい機会って訳か）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She seems quite eager… I see. For Rei too）\n（this is a good opportunity to thank people who helped her.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.5000022888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.5666689078
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "何ニヤニヤしてるんですか？　置いてっちゃいますよ\n出来るだけ、沢山回りたいんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you grinning at? I'll leave you behind.\nI want to visit as many places as possible.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.0666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.0333355744
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.0333355744
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "店長、ご無沙汰してます\nアルバイトしてた頃は本当にお世話になりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Manager‚ it's been a while.\nYou really took care of me when I was working part-time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.0333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "デビューした後も、私達のポスターを貼り出して\nくれて。呼び込みのお仕事までいただいてしまって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even after our debut‚ you put up our posters\nand even gave us promotional work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.9999982196,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5500.001780399998,
          "startTime": 99.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.000002241
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "あ、これ今度のライブのチケットです\n良かったら観に来て下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ these are tickets for our upcoming live.\nPlease come watch if you'd like.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.9000022888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.0000073272
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（怜も店員さん達も、久しぶりに会えたからだろう）\n（凄く嬉しそうだ。随分話が盛り上がってるな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It’s probably because Rei and the staff haven’t seen each other in a while.）\n（They look really happy. The conversation is quite lively.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.8000002543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "特売の日は、つい張り切って大声出しちゃってました\nふふ、肺活量のいいトレーニングになってた気がします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "On sale days‚ I got carried away and shouted loudly.\nFufu‚ I think it was good training for my lungs.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.6333346049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.3666704336
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "え？　この前また、オトクオトクが聞けて嬉しかった？\nぜ、全国ツアーのDVD特典映像、観たんですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? You were happy to hear \"bargain bargain\" again recently?\nD-did you watch the national tour DVD bonus footage!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.1666679382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistore-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistore-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.0333554107
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それでは、名残惜しいですがこの辺で\n怜、そろそろ行こう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ it's hard to leave‚ but we should go now.\nRei‚ let's go.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.200007375,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "はい、{user}さん\n……それじゃあ、また遊びに来ますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ {user}-san.\n…Well then‚ I'll come visit again!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.2333407084,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4833.3576994999985,
          "startTime": 150.0666984079
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_coast-00-000-evening",
      "startTime": 149.8166984079
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "思ってたより遅くなっちゃいましたね\nみんな優しくて、つい話し込んじゃいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It got later than I thought.\nEveryone was so kind‚ I ended up chatting too much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.4333478291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "星見市って、やっぱりいい街ですよね\n地元びいきかもしれませんけど、大好きです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hoshimi City really is a good town‚ isn't it?\nIt might be local bias‚ but I love it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.5333478291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "俺もだ。みんなの始まりの場所だしな。そういえば\n怜が星見プロに入りたいと言ったのも、ここだったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Me too. It's where everyone started. Come to think of it\nthis was where Rei said she wanted to join Hoshimi Pro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.0666709899,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 177.1666846749
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "ここに入ることは出来ますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can I join your agency?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.3333579537,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。それを仕事として、職業として\n両親に紹介出来るのであれば、私は構いません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. As long as I can tell my parents\nit's a job‚ a career‚ I'm fine with that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.6666872179,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5866.676839299998,
          "startTime": 191.5333640572
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_coast-00-000-evening",
      "startTime": 191.3000307239
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "あの時は、突然だったから驚いたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was surprised because it was so sudden back then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.4333620228,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei018.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、すみません……。あの頃は両親から離れて\nなんとか一人でやっていこうと必死で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha‚ sorry… I was desperate to make it\non my own‚ away from my parents….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.3333376566,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei019.m4a",
      "text": "でも、あの時に、この場所で決めたことを\n後悔したことはありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I've never regretted what I decided\nat that time‚ at this place.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.4333376566,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ、ご両親といえば、怜のご家族に送るチケットは\n三枚でいいか？　ご両親と、お兄さんの分",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right‚ speaking of your parents— will 3 tickets be enough\nfor your family? For your parents and your brother.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 215.0333427428,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei020.m4a",
      "text": "あ、いえ、兄は客席で観るのが好きなので\nいつも通り二枚で――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ no. My brother likes watching from the audience\nso two tickets as usual--",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 223.8666760761,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei021.m4a",
      "text": "……って、あれ？　なんで急に兄の分も\n用意してくれたんですか？　今まで言ってなかったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Wait‚ huh? Why are you suddenly offering\nto prepare one for my brother too? I never mentioned him before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 230.2666760761,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "すずから聞いたんだ。怜はお兄さんが大好きだって\nなら、ライブにも来てもらった方がいいんじゃないかと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard from Suzu. That Rei really loves her big brother.\nSo I thought it would be better to have him come to the live too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 239.1333427428,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei022.m4a",
      "text": "と、特別好きとかじゃありませんから！\n普通です。ごく普通の兄妹です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-it's not like I especially love him or anything!\nIt's normal. We're completely normal siblings!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 246.6333427428,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "そうなのか？　「いつも凄く楽しそうに電話してます\nわよ。もうデレデレなくらいで」って言ってたぞ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that so? She said \"She always talks on the phone looking really happy.\nShe's totally smitten with him.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 254.1666740416,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei023.m4a",
      "text": "すずが誇張して言ってるだけです！\n寮に戻ったら、一度懲らしめておかないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu is just exaggerating!\nWhen I get back to the dorm‚ I need to correct her once…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 261.6341446886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "……あまり厳しくしないであげてくれよ。それじゃ\n怜の家族のチケット二枚、明日にでも手配しておくよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Please don't be too hard on her. Well then\nI'll arrange two tickets for Rei's family by tomorrow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 269.9666669208,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei024.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。二枚……あ、でも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. Two tickets… oh‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 274.6000612415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "浮かない顔だけど、どうしたんだ？\n心配ごとでもあるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You look troubled‚ what's wrong?\nIs there something you're worried about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 283.3333335875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei025.m4a",
      "text": "……父は、その日仕事が入っているらしくて\n来れるか分からなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…My father apparently has work that day\nand might not be able to come.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 289.5333335875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……怜のお父さんはお医者さんだったな\nライブに合わせて仕事を休むのは難しいよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… Rei's father is a doctor‚ right?\nIt's difficult to take time off work for a live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 295.8666567483,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-rei026.m4a",
      "text": "急な手術が入ることもあるし、仕方ありませんよ\nだからチケット、一枚無駄にしちゃったらすみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Emergency surgeries can come up‚ so it can't be helped.\nSo if one ticket goes to waste‚ I'm sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 304.1666567483,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_02-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "（……これはご家族の問題だ）\n（俺に出来ることはないが……でも……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…This is a family matter）\n（There's nothing I can do‚ but… still…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 311.3409642114,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}